\[\text{cis } 7 \theta = \text{cis } 225^\circ.\]This equation holds if and only if
\[7 \theta = 225^\circ + 360^\circ k\]for some integer $k$, or
\[\theta = \frac{225^\circ + 360^\circ k}{7}.\][asy]
