Let $\mathbf{v} = \begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ 0 \\ 7 \end{pmatrix},$ and let $\mathbf{p}$ be its projection onto plane $P.$  Note that $\mathbf{v} - \mathbf{p}$ is parallel to $\mathbf{n}.$

